      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/95/115",
      "text": [
        "٩٥. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): لَا يَقِلُّ عَمَلٌ مَعَ التَّقْوَى وَكَيْفَ يَقِلُّ مَا يُتَقَبَّلُ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "95. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: Action accompanied by fear for Allāh does not fail, and how can a thing fail that has been accepted. [1]"
        ]
      }
